      {
        "type": "Markdown",
        "props": {
          "id": "Markdown-aca8710b-23b9-442a-8f53-379c23bd51aa",
          "text": "Proposals",
          "align": "left",
          "measured": false
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Heading",
        "props": {
          "id": "Heading-a7c662cf-d844-490a-b7ad-83402b6338cb",
          "size": "1",
          "text": "Puck Platform Recipe",
          "align": "left",
          "level": "1",
          "maxWidth": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Paragraph",
        "props": {
          "id": "Paragraph-c4249613-4c22-4588-944e-86788763c839",
          "size": "large",
          "text": "A self-hosted, fully-featured page building platform, powered by Puck.",
          "align": "left",
          "maxWidth": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Space",
        "props": {
          "id": "Space-ea6824a6-1a0f-40a4-a8e3-e76eb4e5e08b",
          "size": "08"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Markdown",
        "props": {
          "id": "Markdown-debd6a33-7948-4de9-b98d-9d6dde2e82b6",
          "text": "## Overview\nThe Puck Platform Recipe is a comprehensive, white-label solution for organisations creating intuitive page building systems for their non-technical customers, built by the Puck team.\n\nIt builds on top of the core open-source Puck editing experience, providing a dashboard, database, multi-tenant authentication, templating system and more.\n\n**In early development.**",
          "align": "left",
          "measured": true
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Space",
        "props": {
          "id": "Space-d96fb055-bc93-4413-a7c1-16ac4e984569",
          "size": "07"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Markdown",
        "props": {
          "id": "Markdown-ed853e01-eded-4632-91d0-83e850a95dac",
          "text": "## Details\n\n- [Roadmap & Timeline](/proposals/puck-platform-recipe/roadmap)\n- [License](/proposals/puck-platform-recipe/license)\n- [Early Access Programme](/proposals/puck-platform-recipe/early-access)\n- [Professional Services](/proposals/puck-platform-recipe/professional-services)\n",
          "align": "left",
          "measured": true
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Space",
        "props": {
          "id": "Space-933958f6-b5a3-4df0-90a4-2cce9016f9a2",
          "size": "07"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Heading",
        "props": {
          "id": "Heading-9f5e399b-73ae-477b-96a4-4b5e89db628f",
          "size": "2",
          "text": "Figma Prototype",
          "align": "left",
          "level": "",
          "maxWidth": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Space",
        "props": {
          "id": "Space-b3d9bca4-10e2-4c31-837a-1db3547cdf5e",
          "size": "04"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "Markdown",
        "props": {
          "id": "Markdown-0bfa1d05-589c-44c0-ac42-0218a2d973d2",
          "text": "Indicative, high-level concepts. See [Figma Prototype](https://www.figma.com/proto/kKCpaWHZJzQ8ibccC9IqGO/Puck-Platform-Concept-v0.2?page-id=0%3A1&node-id=0-326&node-type=frame&viewport=971%2C180%2C0.28&t=RVJXZXEz8yInHWsm-1&scaling=scale-down&content-scaling=fixed&starting-point-node-id=0%3A309).",
          "align": "left",
          "measured": false
        }
      }
    ],
